OL,2,MMy shower needs WiFi
OL,4,Cmuurk
OL,5,CSat 11:20-11:50
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GIn 2019, I was sold on the idea that
OL,9,Gmy new shower should have wifi. It
OL,10,Gwould pre-run every morning at 7am,
OL,11,Gguaranteeing hot water. And when I'd
OL,12,Gget out of bed two hours later, I'd
OL,13,Gneed to let it run again. But the
OL,14,Gsystem worked. I was the anomaly. A
OL,15,Gfew years later, the manufacturer
OL,16,Gretired the cloud. My smart shower
OL,17,Gbecame nothing more than a shower. I
OL,18,Gthought nothing of it. For years.
OL,19,GCovid happened and this wasn't even on
OL,20,Gmy list. In a period where people
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
